{
  "text": "Ventral to NA ( Figure 1A , square segment) was a subset of Dbx1 + glutamatergic preB\u00f6 tC SST-expressing respiratory neurons ( Figures 1B and 1C) , essential for breathing movements in adult rats [CITATION_1] . In the ventrolateral medulla of adult Dbx1-ChR2 ( Figures 1A-1C ) and SST-ChR2 ( Figures 1D and  1F ) mice, tdTomato predominately overlapped with the distribution of SST-expressing neurons that demark the preB\u00f6 tC [CITATION_2] .",
